>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"&quot;No Russian&quot; is a controversial level in the 2009 first-person shooter game Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2. In the level, the player controls Joseph Allen, an undercover CIA agent who participates in a mass shooting at a Moscow airport to gain the trust of a Russian terrorist group. The leader of the terrorists, Vladimir Makarov, tells his co-conspirators, &quot;Remember, no Russian&quot;, implying that speaking Russian would reveal their ethnic origins and affiliation to the Russian ultranationalists. At the end of the level, Makarov kills Allen and reveals that he intended for Russian officials to find Allen's body and believe that the attack was instigated by the United States."},{"pid":"65979b852d56b4f3603e74d6e24141590a6be924","tid":1896753,"uid":39492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"點解人哋要道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如整個全球最大精神病院俾支那啦，呢啲自卑心重嘅怨婦真係好撚柒煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n道你老母咩！理好自己個武漢肺炎先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b33c70dbeb66809abdb4d4f7f9c81b8bdbe43ab","tid":1896753,"uid":78651,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"38c0b8bbfee122c42ce2124485d17c87f62b21b0","tid":1896753,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"09f244b927a6d64d648e8c8ddcdbef5415db464b","tid":1896753,"uid":2429,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OWgNH7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OWgNH7.png&h=5b99cfa7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T10:28